### 6.2 Device Login is Different
Biometric devices authenticate via HMAC-SHA256 signature, not JWT. Device has `device_id` and shared secret stored in AWS Secrets Manager. Every POST to `/api/v1/attendance/biometric-event` includes `X-Device-ID` and `X-Signature` headers. Service verifies signature before processing.

